OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales Andrew John
OL,4,Cretires following Bangor Cathedral
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FThe Archbishop of Wales has announced
OL,8,Fhe will retire with immediate effect.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Andrew John confirmed
OL,11,Fhe would also step down from his role
OL,12,Fas Bishop of Bangor on 31st August.
OL,14,FHe said, "I would very much like to
OL,15,Fthank the clergy and congregations of
OL,16,Fthis wonderful diocese before I retire
OL,17,Fand I will be in touch again about the
OL,18,Fway in which this might happen."
