OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales Andrew John
OL,4,Cretires following Bangor Cathedral
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FIn May, two summary reports were
OL,8,Fpublished after concerns about Bangor
OL,9,FCathedral. One detailed reports of
OL,10,Finappropriate behaviour, lack of
OL,11,Fboundaries and excessive alcohol
OL,12,Fconsumption.
OL,14,FAt the time, the Church in Wales said
OL,15,Fit takes safeguarding extremely
OL,16,Fseriously. The Archbishop said the
OL,17,Ffindings "offer (...) opportunity for
OL,18,Fchange". There was no suggestion that
OL,19,FAndrew John behaved inappropriately.
