OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales Andrew John
OL,4,Cretires following Bangor Cathedral
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FAndrew John became the Bishop of
OL,8,FBangor in 2008. He was appointed as
OL,9,FArchbishop in 2021, taking over from
OL,10,FJohn Davies.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Archbishop Andrew John
OL,13,Fsaid, "I am writing to you to announce
OL,14,Fmy immediate retirement today as
OL,15,FArchbishop of Wales. I also intend to
OL,16,Fretire as Bishop of Bangor on August
OL,17,F31st.
