OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales Andrew John
OL,4,Cretires following Bangor Cathedral
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FIt has been an enormous joy to serve
OL,8,Fin the Church in Wales for over 35
OL,9,Fyears. I cannot thank you enough for
OL,10,Fthe privilege of working at your side
OL,11,Ffor the sake of our Saviour Jesus
OL,12,FChrist."
OL,14,FProfessor Medwin Hughes, Chair of the
OL,15,FRepresentative Body of the Church in
OL,16,FWales, said, "I want to place on
OL,17,Frecord my sincere gratitude for all he
OL,18,Fhas achieved, together with my
OL,19,Fadmiration for the integrity of his
OL,20,Fministry to the people of Wales."
